<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个公主都拥有自己的小花园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个公主把她的花园做成了鲸鱼的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个公主把她的花园做成了贝壳的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主们在花园里放满了她们在沉船里找到的奇怪东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，小美人鱼的花园很简单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有红色的花和一个人类男孩雕像。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个雕像是她妈妈的，小美人鱼很爱它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当姐姐们在她们花园里玩儿的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼静静地坐在她的花园里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看着那个男孩雕像，她对人类和地上世界充满了好奇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“地上世界是什么样子的？”有一天，她问奶奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，小宝贝，那里有很多值得看的！”智慧人鱼说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那里有树林，当空气变冷时，就会变颜色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，树叶就会掉到地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，就会下雪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪？”小美人鱼说，“雪是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪是由小冰花组成的。”奶奶回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在冬天，这些小冰花从天上落下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是在夏天，绿草覆盖土地，到处充满了浓郁的花香。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听起来很棒。”小美人鱼说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在这里，我们的树没有变化，花也没有香味。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>智慧人鱼告诉小美人鱼更多的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在地上世界，你可以仰望天空，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>清楚地看见太阳、月亮和星星。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145474</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小鸟在树之间飞来飞去，唱着好听的歌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给我讲讲动物吧，奶奶。”小美人鱼恳求说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就像我说的那样，有些动物飞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，很多动物有四条腿，在地上走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175873</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人类用两条腿走，他们非常擅长造东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175874</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们盖了很多房子，房子组成了村庄。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼想听得更多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们也会造船，是吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，是的，小宝贝。”奶奶说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，你已经知道了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道，但是我想听关于人类的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在上面航海，离我们很近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，他们的世界看起来很遥远。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，人类跟我们很不一样。”奶奶说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215933</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们不像人鱼这么长寿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们能活三百年！但是，人类有灵魂。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“灵魂是什么？”小美人鱼问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不知道，小宝贝。”奶奶回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听说灵魂能永生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，人类也不真正了解灵魂是什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不管它是什么，我觉得它一定很特别。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想了解人类的一切！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等你十五岁了，你会知道的。”奶奶说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能游到海面上去，看有些船来来往往。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，我想现在就去！”小美人鱼恳求说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要有耐心。再过五年，就轮到你了。”奶奶笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，你会发现，宝贝，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们海底的家比别的任何地方都好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几年过去了，姐姐们都去过地上世界。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，她得等待。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在晴朗的夜晚，她抬头看着月亮和星星。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当一个阴影掠过她们时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她知道那是一艘船从她们头顶开过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼渴望地把胳膊伸向船底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>总有一天，她将触摸到地上世界。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>